msgid ""
"The release of 4.3BSD added the Xerox Network Systems (XNS) protocol suite, "
"partly building on work done at the University of Maryland and at Cornell "
"University.  This suite was needed to connect isolated machines that could "
"not communicate using TCP/IP."
msgstr ""
"El lanzamiento de 4.3BSD agregó la suite de protocolos Xerox Network Systems "
"(XNS), en parte basándose en el trabajo realizado en la Universidad de "
"Maryland y en la Universidad de Cornell. Esta suite era necesaria para "
"conectar máquinas aisladas que no podían comunicarse mediante TCP / IP."

